sequenceDiagram
  participant U as 用户
  participant CLI as CLI 入口
  participant H as Harness
  participant M as Model
  participant TR as Tool Runtime
  participant FS as 项目环境
  participant S as Session Store

  U->>CLI: 修复失败测试
  CLI->>H: 创建或恢复 session
  H->>S: 读取历史、规则、预算
  H->>M: 发送本轮上下文
  M-->>H: 返回工具意图
  H->>H: 校验权限和参数
  H->>TR: 执行受控工具
  TR->>FS: 读文件或跑测试
  FS-->>TR: 返回结果
  TR-->>H: observation
  H->>S: 追加事件日志
  H->>M: 下一轮上下文
